<br/>
We, {!pocPackage.Client_Company_Name} (the "Creditor"), are writing to notify you that {!pocPackage.CFG_Office_Name} (the "Servicer") will be administering the processing and filing (and all related matters thereto) of all new bankruptcy or consumer proposals under the <i> Bankruptcy and Insolvency Act </i>(Canada) from and after March 1, 2018 in respect of which you are appointed as bankruptcy trustee for any customers of the Creditor (including customers of the Creditor’s affiliates and customers of the Creditor under the Scotiabank PrivateLabel Cards, each as listed on Schedule A attached hereto). 
<br/><br/>
We request that all correspondence and documentation, including without limitation, creditor packages, statement of affairs, voting letters, requests for additional documentation and approvals / notice of disallowance of claims, in relation to the above noted accounts be directed to the Servicer at the following contact details:
<br/><br/>
<div style="width:100%; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11px;">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{!pocPackage.CFG_Office_Name}.
